1. Ona* meri* pola metra. (She measures half a meter.)
2. Imamo* meru* da se poboljšamo. (We have a measure to improve.)
3. Ona se* meri* sa visinom. (She measures herself with height.)
4. Oni su* merili* dva puta. (They measured twice.)
5. Ima* meru* učinkovitosti. (There is a measure of efficiency.)